### ---------------- AUTH ---------------- ###

### Register
POST http://localhost:3000/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "test@example.com",
  "password": "password123",
  "username": "TestUser",
  "profilePic": "http://example.com/avatar.png"
}

### Login
POST http://localhost:3000/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "test@example.com",
  "password": "password123"
}

### ---------------- USER ---------------- ###

### Update Profile
PUT http://localhost:3000/user/update-profile
Authorization: Bearer your_jwt_token_here
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "UpdatedUsername",
  "profilePic": "http://example.com/new-avatar.png"
}

### ---------------- RECIPES ---------------- ###

### Get all recipes (with pagination)
GET http://localhost:3000/recipes?page=1&limit=6

### Get a specific recipe
GET http://localhost:3000/recipes/RECIPE_ID

### Create a new recipe
POST http://localhost:3000/recipes
Authorization: Bearer your_jwt_token_here
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Spaghetti Carbonara",
  "description": "Classic Italian pasta dish",
  "ingredients": ["Pasta", "Eggs", "Pancetta", "Parmesan"],
  "steps": ["Boil pasta", "Cook pancetta", "Combine with eggs and cheese"],
  "cookingTime": 30,
  "imageCover": "http://localhost:3000/uploads/file-123.png"
}

### Update a recipe
PATCH http://localhost:3000/recipes/RECIPE_ID
Authorization: Bearer your_jwt_token_here
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "cookingTime": 25
}

### Delete a recipe
DELETE http://localhost:3000/recipes/RECIPE_ID
Authorization: Bearer your_jwt_token_here

### Toggle Favorite
POST http://localhost:3000/recipes/RECIPE_ID/favorite
Authorization: Bearer your_jwt_token_here

